<p>Reports incorrect injection points: fields, methods, and parameters annotated with <code>@Inject</code> that violate the CDI specification.</p>

<p>Requirements for fields:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Cannot be static or final</li>
  <li>Cannot be annotated with <code>@Produces</code></li>
</ul>

<p>Requirements for methods with injection:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Cannot be static or abstract</li>
  <li>Cannot have parameters with <code>@Disposes</code> and <code>@Observes</code> annotations</li>
</ul>
</body>
